  <name>systemd Pilot</name>
  <summary>Manage systemd services</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      systemd Pilot is a GTK4 application that helps you manage systemd services with a user-friendly interface. Features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>View and manage system and user services</li>
      <li>Start, stop, restart services</li>
      <li>Enable or disable services</li>
      <li>View detailed service status</li>
      <li>Filter services by status</li>
      <li>Search functionality</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
